Dear our Guests,

EXPLORE TURKEY WITH ASTARTETOURS!!
	
Hotel Reservations: 
You will find more than 200 hotels all over Turkey, which have been carefully selected.
Through our reservation system we are able to book more than 1.000 hotels arround Europe.
 
Tours 
Hosted Programs, sightseeing tours, escorted tours or cruise programs.
We have tours on set dates each year or we can organize special itineraries for the independant traveller or small groups!!
 

Rent-A-Car:
Travelling on your own pace in Turkey! We have a range of vehicles on offer to choose from. They may be hired in all major cities. 
Your car can be made available at the airport or your hotel for collection!!

Visit our web-site!!

www.astartetours.com

Kind Regards
Astarte Tours
